    <span class="l1"><b>VINAY</b></span>
    <span class="l2"><b>KOPPADA</b></span>
  </h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">I design <strong>posters, flyers, brochures and menus</strong> that get noticed on a wall, in a hand, or on a scroll. Real client work below — food brands, fitness, drinks, and corporate identity.</p>

  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div>role<strong>Graphic Designer</strong></div>
    <div>phone<strong><a href="tel:+918143644822">+91 81436 44822</a></strong></div>
    <div>email<strong><a href="mailto:vinaykoppada7@gmail.com">vinaykoppada7@gmail.com</a></strong></div>
